With 85,486 total #COVID19 cases, Philippines now has more confirmed cases than mainland China, where the disease was first reported.

On Wednesday, the country also surpassed UP researchers' projection of 85,000 cases by the end of July. https://t.co/Ee33hVS6Ox https://t.co/YaeYi2xPAL
